    <node id="ASME Boiler and Pressure Vessel Code">
      <data key="d0">ASME Boiler and Pressure Vessel Code</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">ASME Boiler and Pressure Vessel Code is a standard for the design, fabrication, and inspection of boilers and pressure vessels.&lt;SEP&gt;ASME Boiler and Pressure Vessel Code is a standard for boilers and pressure vessels.&lt;SEP&gt;The ASME Boiler and Pressure Vessel Code provides allowable stress, ultimate tensile strength, and yield strength values for materials.&lt;SEP&gt;The ASME Boiler and Pressure Vessel Code is a standard for the design, fabrication, inspection, and testing of boilers, pressure vessels, and related accessories.</data>
