      <data key="d0">Working Pressures by Classes, psig</data>
      <data key="d1">category</data>
      <data key="d2">Working Pressures by Classes, psig categorizes pressure ratings for different temperature classes.&lt;SEP&gt;Working pressures by classes, measured in pounds per square inch gauge (psig), are provided for various temperature ranges.&lt;SEP&gt;Working Pressures by Classes, psig is a concept describing the pressure ratings at different temperature classes.&lt;SEP&gt;Working Pressures by Classes, psig is a concept describing the pressure ratings for different temperature classes.&lt;SEP&gt;Working Pressures by Classes, psig, show the permissible working pressures for different temperature classes.</data>
