    <node id="Holes">
      <data key="d0">Holes</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Holes are openings in pipe fittings.&lt;SEP&gt;Holes refer to specific drilling dimensions for flange fittings as described in the ASME B16.5-2013 standard.&lt;SEP&gt;Holes are mentioned in the ASME B16.5-2013 standard as part of the flanged fittings.</data>
