    <node id="IHS">
      <data key="d0">IHS</data>
      <data key="d1">organization</data>
      <data key="d2">IHS is the organization that provides access to and licensing services for ASME standards and documents, including the ASME B16.5-2013 standard. Specifically, IHS is under license with ASME to provide the pressure-temperature ratings table, the document, the data, and the copyrighted material related to ASME standards and documents. IHS also provides licensing for the reproduction and networking of certain ASME documents, such as ASME B16.5-2013, and offers licensing services for the ASME standard document, ensuring compliance with ASME International guidelines.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-366d21bccd71c76a4c780fde0cfa7e08&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e08aa81b5449d47c5a323ae8a58ce735&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-91fb20c66854d4220d2bb89dece25b26&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-02c8f43c223cee2154c66d0d4ab324af&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e6dd99d0d594bbdd5db11e31461478c9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8c9531d076f004c30f7355a51c50bbeb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-920ee37a2f41f0148b3f2c484edae395&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1261f13c12701dc16f49237f702e1cab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2c1e39e4ae6c4190629baeb4a23e7884&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7d361c91bf3e9c4f81478ff64f43f6fa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-87960735c6e595f042bd664132512ec0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9010b0d631cf0ee8f2876c69fd7db43d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-69f5dfdb3c7a4f92fcc61b0351584206&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8e7b456ed825c2e777586a3d95199f23&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-376c9d90c67ab8cb5f4d7bef0d9995e3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e5e7d6611dd06e592bef62dbd08dc044&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c1c1f70080d9d2a6ea93b5640ca8cea0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bbc4f25f5a21132e1571d8baa298136c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-caecc4edbb295cee17a2e0533066f3b0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8c26f486bf229ab399297201ce84ec2f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f67cfb71cad6bdaadc291b0dfadb7d87&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fb7c5babdbcd75bdf9752cd67bcadc21&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0def5c7323fd1839a8729ecb6b306f46&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-585c1c45925ddd2546b76b97e57456ed&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-94e58312a7e84066f13cc4e7ad9465d9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-47d30b91c8304767d9ee5dee433bb6cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d88c25523fb6a395eb9e2724eb0719d5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-83ab283e30659c933554a033613d2618&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bc5fbf3f97e8bcfd2b79a4ca1deaa326&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-685be4db70f3b18d8a8fac56db2cfaa3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b16d82598801637712b84cc1424040fd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1873d06e9a30c27b355fbcaa093fe77d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d633ba5ade581e3474128d750fee5dad&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5c8a2582fdf55b244cf7d4892e61cc9f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4a2aa51a49817516d8e488a9d7c544a9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-de39ca8c7c360d8542b6e7b848f32671&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-82774a230daae46ca5bfd3f0231302b9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-43a75c51519a7791b8c4227900b22d57&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e75e86bfb0de38b435f7fe46c6bdc923&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe557ad0e335444e461df848f9e28d6b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cd6664ea75cb3