    <node id="Pipe">
      <data key="d0">Pipe</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Pipe is a cylindrical tube used for conveying fluids or gases.&lt;SEP&gt;Pipe is a component discussed in the standard, related to flange dimensions and joint types.&lt;SEP&gt;Pipe is a tubular section used for conveying fluids or gases.&lt;SEP&gt;Pipe is a component in the fabrication of flanged fittings.&lt;SEP&gt;Pipe is a tubular conductor used for conveying fluids or gases.&lt;SEP&gt;Pipe is a long hollow cylinder used to convey fluids or gases.&lt;SEP&gt;Pipe is a long hollow cylinder used for conveying fluids or gases.</data>
