      <data key="d0">50°C (125°F)</data>
      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">50°C (125°F) is the maximum temperature for the test fluid.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-37388fa1515f3cf7a8930b2598d5740e</data>
