    <node id="Minimum Slope">
      <data key="d0">Minimum Slope</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Minimum Slope is a design parameter for the bevels in welding neck flanges.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-37388fa1515f3cf7a8930b2598d5740e</data>
      <data key="d4">ASME B16.5-2013.pdf</data>
      <data key="d5">1776329034</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="ASME B16.5-2013">
      <data key="d0">ASME B16.5-2013</data>
      <data key="d1">standard</data>
      <data key="d2">ASME B16.5-2013 is a standard document published by ASME International, which covers pipe flanges and flanged fittings. This standard was approved by the American National Standards Institute on February 5, 2013. It provides detailed specifications for flanges, including pressure-temperature ratings, materials, dimensions, and testing methods. ASME B16.5-2013 also includes specifications for flanged fittings, such as dimensions and configurations, and covers various classes of flanges, including Class 150, 300, 600, 1500, and 2500. Additionally, it specifies flange bolting dimensions, flange facings, ring-joint facings dimensions, and flange sealing solutions. The standard also addresses the design, fabrication, and installation of pipe flanges, flanged fittings, and pipe threads.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-8141fd83406f7d50dac6f93c308cba1a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-366d21bccd71c76a4c780fde0cfa7e08&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c551c98db1e7353686af155387c310fd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-51676999d6498cdd7ba881a128f7d63f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0f2fde18096ae54093e820b71568eac&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-09c7747fb737fd6e9b29eb11eb4c7556&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-37388fa1515f3cf7a8930b2598d5740e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-91fb20c66854d4220d2bb89dece25b26&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-02c8f43c223cee2154c66d0d4ab324af&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c5f5e2c6bb85dac52bdfa7453796ec77&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e6dd99d0d594bbdd5db11e31461478c9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-920ee37a2f41f0148b3f2c484edae395&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1261f13c12701dc16f49237f702e1cab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2c1e39e4ae6c4190629baeb4a23e7884&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-98e40539084cbdf59ac9013514ddab83&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7d361c91bf3e9c4f81478ff64f43f6fa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-87960735c6e595f042bd664132512ec0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f58e723d717e78901685416a73eb271b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-69f5dfdb3c7a4f92fcc61b0351584206&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8e7b456ed825c2e777586a3d95199f23&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-376c9d90c67ab8cb5f4d7bef0d9995e3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e5e7d6611dd06e592bef62dbd08dc044&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-20a6e7f0600d773fff6396f54c63b132&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e8f5c9d7666d5ca64fad9fe5409f4a67&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bbc4f25f5a21132e1571d8baa298136c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-efde1d42acf7b7dcd9aa6c8b3872b2cc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-caecc4edbb295cee17a2e0533066f3b0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8c26f486bf229ab399297201ce84ec2f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-157dd67058da951e9c5cc75c8d297ca5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f67cfb71cad6bdaadc291b0dfadb7d87&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cfef247a2504069e002ce01be642a1e9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8169ff4613bfdf221fbd8f42873b7f64&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4303e33e6d61d4207aeb4ef2e5ef35ea&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0def5c7323fd1839a8729ecb6b306f46&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-585c1c45925ddd2546b76b97e57456ed&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b181980b1dcef22dc859d6b6b9c724e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-97992c13bd15395adccdb59249057965&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5e85bee1a6414b667d34d9e3ddb49f16&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-94e58312a7e84066f13cc4e7ad9465d9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0f78928bda50367f51793fceb76dd206&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-47d30b91c8304