    <node id="Welding Neck Flanges">
      <data key="d0">Welding Neck Flanges</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Welding Neck Flanges are flanges with a hub at the welding end, designed to ensure adequate flange hub thickness.&lt;SEP&gt;Welding Neck Flanges are a type of flange with a neck for welding.&lt;SEP&gt;Welding Neck Flanges are components used in the fabrication of flanged fittings.</data>
