      <data key="d1">standard</data>
      <data key="d2">ASTM A217, Table 1 lists the permissible elements for certain materials.&lt;SEP&gt;ASTM A217, Table 1 is a reference table for material specifications.&lt;SEP&gt;ASTM A217, Table 1 is a reference standard for material specifications.&lt;SEP&gt;ASTM A217, Table 1 is a reference table listing permissible elements for certain materials.</data>
