    <node id="Mandatory Appendix II">
      <data key="d0">Mandatory Appendix II</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Mandatory Appendix II is a specific appendix referenced in technical specifications, particularly within the context of the ASME Boiler and Pressure Vessel Code. It contains a variety of detailed information and tables that provide specifications and guidelines for various aspects of pipe flange design and construction. Specifically, it includes tables listing pressure-temperature ratings for different systems, metallurgical requirements, minimum wall thicknesses, and other relevant specifications. Additionally, it provides detailed information on stud bolt lengths, gasket dimensions, and flange preparations and dimensions, including both flange facings and ring joint facings. The appendix also references ASME B16.5-2013 specifications and provides dimensions in inch units for pipe flanges. Furthermore, it offers additional mandatory information related to the dimensions of pipe flanges and contains tables and figures that are referenced in the main document, ensuring comprehensive coverage of the necessary technical details.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-c551c98db1e7353686af155387c310fd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9010b0d631cf0ee8f2876c69fd7db43d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-157dd67058da951e9c5cc75c8d297ca5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b181980b1dcef22dc859d6b6b9c724e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b8d7fbf71d349a93ea469c5166b31e89&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d9d6f8ad3531ac0840bf5ba01dc89ab8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9ab03faa83213dbc994bff8e8951d1d7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ab71f5f8294a0ded93d84d65df8a8aeb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-baede3ecfe2637d28f283b80b0cc9cf0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-27138329aa3769f926ca7ebbcd2c8891&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-43e5005d4928be252c7355587c71a1aa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-28281081225db05b8b7d5f11501b022d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7f206c1ddea4cbeb2d1fc9d3ca987bee</data>
