    <node id="Reducing Fittings">
      <data key="d0">Reducing Fittings</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Reducing fittings are used to connect pipes of different diameters.&lt;SEP&gt;Reducing Fittings are a type of fitting mentioned in the document.&lt;SEP&gt;Reducing Fittings are fittings with specific dimensions that change in size.&lt;SEP&gt;Reducing fittings are fittings that reduce the size of pipes and are detailed in paragraphs 6.2.3 and 6.4.2.2.&lt;SEP&gt;Reducing Fittings are fittings that reduce the size of pipes and have specific dimensions as described in the document.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-ccbc09bef8fd93e5314dec1dbec481cb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-439097792cec97ce9b1b0fb080fa39fc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b8d7fbf71d349a93ea469c5166b31e89&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a18d7afa11aad3756a7707e009d78fc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eb33e5534b0b007ab3fc536bdf30e65c</data>
