    <node id="Ring Joint Facing Dimensions">
      <data key="d0">Ring Joint Facing Dimensions</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Ring Joint Facing Dimensions are dimensions related to flanges.&lt;SEP&gt;Ring Joint Facing Dimensions are specific measurements for the facing of ring joints as detailed in Table II-5 of Mandatory Appendix II.&lt;SEP&gt;Ring Joint Facing Dimensions are specific measurements for the ring joint groove.&lt;SEP&gt;Ring joint facing dimensions are provided in Table II-5 of Mandatory Appendix II.&lt;SEP&gt;Ring Joint Facing Dimensions are specific measurements for fittings as described in Table II-5 of Mandatory Appendix II.&lt;SEP&gt;Ring joint facing dimensions are specific measurements mentioned in technical specifications.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-ccbc09bef8fd93e5314dec1dbec481cb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9010b0d631cf0ee8f2876c69fd7db43d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-439097792cec97ce9b1b0fb080fa39fc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a18d7afa11aad3756a7707e009d78fc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bca2cf22c89695d4ce65335b23352b32&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eb33e5534b0b007ab3fc536bdf30e65c</data>
