      <data key="d2">Tee is a type of flanged fitting described in the ASME B16.5-2013 standard.&lt;SEP&gt;Tee is a type of fitting mentioned in the ASME B16.5-2013 standard.&lt;SEP&gt;Tee is a type of flanged fitting.&lt;SEP&gt;Tee is a flanged fitting that divides the flow of fluid into two directions.&lt;SEP&gt;Tee is a type of fitting that splits a pipe into two directions.&lt;SEP&gt;Tee is a type of fitting that connects three pipes and has specific dimensions as described in the document.</data>
