    <node id="Eccentric">
      <data key="d0">Eccentric</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Eccentric refers to a specific type of pipe fitting.&lt;SEP&gt;Eccentric refers to a condition where the axis of a pipe fitting is offset from the centerline.&lt;SEP&gt;Eccentric is a type of flanged fitting mentioned in the ASME B16.5-2013 standard.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-87960735c6e595f042bd664132512ec0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-824f6bfcd2b200f81ced17dd1feea1ae&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-40e7dd88714557fcaa5b58340393bd06</data>
