      <data key="d0">45-deg Lateral</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">45-deg Lateral is a type of lateral mentioned in the context of dimensions and specifications.&lt;SEP&gt;45-deg Lateral is a type of flanged fitting described in the ASME B16.5-2013 standard.&lt;SEP&gt;45-deg Lateral is a type of lateral elbow fitting with a 45-degree angle.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-87960735c6e595f042bd664132512ec0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2cfed12e16e2f62a0ac34d806ce49eea&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eb33e5534b0b007ab3fc536bdf30e65c</data>
