      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Long Radius refers to a specific type of pipe fitting.&lt;SEP&gt;Long Radius is a type of elbow mentioned in the context of dimensions and specifications.&lt;SEP&gt;Long Radius is a concept related to the design of flanged fittings described in the ASME B16.5-2013 standard.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-87960735c6e595f042bd664132512ec0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-824f6bfcd2b200f81ced17dd1feea1ae&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2cfed12e16e2f62a0ac34d806ce49eea</data>
