      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Center-to-contact surface refers to the distance from the center of a flange to its contact surface.&lt;SEP&gt;Center-to-Contact Surface is a measurement related to the dimensions of flanged fittings.&lt;SEP&gt;Center-to-Contact Surface is a measurement from the center of the fitting to the contact surface of the flange.&lt;SEP&gt;Center-to-Contact Surface is a measurement related to the dimensions of fittings.&lt;SEP&gt;Center-to-contact surface dimensions are detailed in paragraphs 6.2.3 and 6.4.2.2.&lt;SEP&gt;Center-to-contact surface refers to a specific dimension measurement in technical specifications.</data>
