    <node id="Elbow">
      <data key="d0">Elbow</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Elbow is a type of pipe fitting mentioned in the context of dimensions and specifications.&lt;SEP&gt;Elbow is a pipe fitting used in plumbing and industrial applications.&lt;SEP&gt;Elbow is a pipe fitting that changes the direction of the flow, commonly used in plumbing and industrial piping.&lt;SEP&gt;Elbow is a type of fitting mentioned in the ASME B16.5-2013 standard.&lt;SEP&gt;Elbow is a type of flanged fitting.&lt;SEP&gt;Elbow is a type of fitting that changes the direction of a pipe.</data>
