    <node id="Class 300 Flanged Fittings">
      <data key="d0">Class 300 Flanged Fittings</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Class 300 Flanged Fittings are a specific class of flanged fittings with a higher pressure rating than Class 150.&lt;SEP&gt;Class 300 Flanged Fittings are a category of pipe fittings mentioned in the context of dimensions and specifications.&lt;SEP&gt;Class 300 Flanged Fittings are a specific type of pipe fitting with a pressure rating of 300 pounds per square inch.&lt;SEP&gt;Class 300 Flanged Fittings are a specific type of flanged fitting described in the ASME B16.5-2013 standard.</data>
