      <data key="d0">275</data>
      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">275 is a working pressure at -20 to 100°F in the pressure-temperature ratings table.&lt;SEP&gt;275 psi is the working pressure at 150°F for the 33Ni–42Fe–21Cr B564 Gr. N08800 material.&lt;SEP&gt;275 is a pressure value in pounds per square inch gauge (psig).&lt;SEP&gt;275 is a numerical data point.</data>
