      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Bolts are fasteners used to secure flanged joints.&lt;SEP&gt;Bolts are mentioned in the ASME B16.5-2013 standard, specifying their outside diameter and number.&lt;SEP&gt;Bolts are fasteners used to join components together.</data>
