      <data key="d0">Templates</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Templates are guides for drilling bolt holes in flanges.&lt;SEP&gt;Templates for drilling are provided in the ASME B16.5-2013 standard, offering guidance for flange and fitting installation.&lt;SEP&gt;Templates are used to guide the drilling of bolt holes in the flange.</data>
