      <data key="d1">person</data>
      <data key="d2">Purchaser is mentioned as someone who specifies certain dimensions, such as the inside diameter of pipe.&lt;SEP&gt;Purchaser is an individual or organization responsible for specifying requirements.&lt;SEP&gt;Purchaser specifies certain dimensions as required.&lt;SEP&gt;Purchaser is mentioned as someone who may specify certain dimensions or requirements.&lt;SEP&gt;Purchaser is mentioned in the ASME B16.5-2013 standard, indicating that certain specifications need to be specified by the purchaser.&lt;SEP&gt;The Purchaser is the entity responsible for specifying certain requirements.&lt;SEP&gt;Purchaser is the entity responsible for specifying certain requirements.</data>
