      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">A182 Gr. F310 is a specific grade of material with defined pressure-temperature ratings.&lt;SEP&gt;A182 Gr. F310 is a material designation used in forgings, castings, and plates.&lt;SEP&gt;A182 Gr. F310 is a material designation mentioned in the table.</data>
