    <node id="Flange Facing Finish">
      <data key="d0">Flange Facing Finish</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Flange Facing Finish refers to the surface finish of flanges, particularly for raised face and large male and female flanges.&lt;SEP&gt;Flange Facing Finish refers to the surface finish requirements for flanges to ensure proper gasket sealing.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-e0e55f15f4fdc887c0046610b4244415&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7d620a92f42ccd64b2c87242914a0398</data>
