    </node>
    <node id="Reducing Threaded and Slip-On Flanges">
      <data key="d0">Reducing Threaded and Slip-On Flanges</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Reducing Threaded and Slip-On Flanges are types of flanges used in classes 150 through 2500.&lt;SEP&gt;Reducing Threaded and Slip-On Flanges are flanges that allow for reduction in pipe size and are installed using threading and slip-on methods.&lt;SEP&gt;Reducing Threaded and Slip-On Flanges are flanges designed to reduce the size of pipes.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-e0e55f15f4fdc887c0046610b4244415&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cbee673be506ab63f82af3e68ebebcd1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9dc638f0d9855d44e84fb84b1e17f97e</data>
