    <node id="Class 150 Flanges">
      <data key="d0">Class 150 Flanges</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Class 150 Flanges are a specific class of flanges with a particular pressure rating.&lt;SEP&gt;Table 8 details the dimensions of Class 150 flanges.&lt;SEP&gt;Class 150 Flanges are described in the ASME B16.5-2013 standard, detailing their dimensions and specifications.&lt;SEP&gt;Class 150 Flanges are pipe fittings with specific dimensions and properties as described in ASME B16.5-2013.&lt;SEP&gt;Class 150 Flanges are described in ASME B16.5-2013 and have specific dimensions and tolerances.</data>
