      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Blind Flange is a type of flange used to close off the end of a pipe.&lt;SEP&gt;A Blind Flange is a flat, circular flange used to close off the end of a pipe or vessel.&lt;SEP&gt;Blind Flange is a type of flange used to close off a pipeline.&lt;SEP&gt;Blind Flange is a type of flange that covers the end of a pipe or vessel.</data>
