    <node id="Spot Facing">
      <data key="d0">Spot Facing</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Spot Facing is a method of finishing the surface of a pipe fitting.&lt;SEP&gt;Spot facing is a machining operation performed on the end face of a pipe or flange to ensure a clean and flat surface for welding.&lt;SEP&gt;Spot Facing is a type of flange finishing process.&lt;SEP&gt;Spot facing is a process where the flange face is machined to ensure a tight seal.&lt;SEP&gt;Spot facing is described in paragraph 6.6.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-4303e33e6d61d4207aeb4ef2e5ef35ea&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cbee673be506ab63f82af3e68ebebcd1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a18d7afa11aad3756a7707e009d78fc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-de39ca8c7c360d8542b6e7b848f32671&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-57eadb61afc03dbca89ec4177318d30f</data>
