      <data key="d0">Threaded Flange</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Threaded flange is a type of flange with screw threads on the outside edge for joining to threaded pipe.&lt;SEP&gt;Threaded Flange is a type of flange with threads for connection as detailed in ASME B16.5-2013.&lt;SEP&gt;Threaded Flange is a type of flange with threaded connections.&lt;SEP&gt;Threaded flange is a type of flange where the connection is made through threading.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-5e85bee1a6414b667d34d9e3ddb49f16&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cbee673be506ab63f82af3e68ebebcd1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-de39ca8c7c360d8542b6e7b848f32671&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e253e99ebed9a87e642e60132b8f53d9</data>
      <data key="d4">ASME B16.5-2013.pdf</data>
      <data key="d5">1776329041</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Slip-On Flange">
      <data key="d0">Slip-On Flange</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Slip-On Flange is a type of flange described in ASME B16.5-2013.&lt;SEP&gt;Slip-On Flange is a type of flange that slips over the pipe and is detailed in ASME B16.5-2013.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-5e85bee1a6414b667d34d9e3ddb49f16&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4a2aa51a49817516d8e488a9d7c544a9</data>
