    <node id="−29 to 38">
      <data key="d0">−29 to 38</data>
      <data key="d1">temperaturerange</data>
      <data key="d2">This temperature range is applicable for certain material groups and pressure classes.&lt;SEP&gt;The temperature range from −29 to 38 °C is specified for certain pressure ratings.&lt;SEP&gt;−29 to 38 is a temperature range in degrees Celsius.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-94e58312a7e84066f13cc4e7ad9465d9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c38d97b0aceca7464ebbbd9a7db0c8d9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f9faa893029db6f5b871493c6380ddac&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-30fa107e1afe5b6cba81caa3af7a1ab4</data>
