    <node id="Table 8">
      <data key="d0">Table 8</data>
      <data key="d1">content</data>
      <data key="d2">Table 8 provides minimum thread lengths for reducing flanges.&lt;SEP&gt;Table 8 contains dimensions of Class 150 Flanges, continuing from the previous table.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-47d30b91c8304767d9ee5dee433bb6cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ab71f5f8294a0ded93d84d65df8a8aeb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1540605fd2ac6288ffd67a864ba6096a</data>
