    <node id="Welding End Bevel">
      <data key="d0">Welding End Bevel</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Welding End Bevel is a preparation for welding in flange connections.&lt;SEP&gt;Welding end bevel is a technique used in preparing pipe ends for welding.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-cbee673be506ab63f82af3e68ebebcd1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f024c3dde67312e25d76e977dcb7753c</data>
