    <node id="Reducing Welding Neck Flanges">
      <data key="d0">Reducing Welding Neck Flanges</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Reducing Welding Neck Flanges are flanges that allow for reduction in pipe size and have a welded neck for connecting pipes.&lt;SEP&gt;Reducing Welding Neck Flanges are flanges designed to reduce the size of pipes with a welding neck.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-cbee673be506ab63f82af3e68ebebcd1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9dc638f0d9855d44e84fb84b1e17f97e</data>
