      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Point height is a dimension related to the design of flanges and fittings.&lt;SEP&gt;Point height is a specific measurement related to the height of points in flange bolt holes.&lt;SEP&gt;Point height is a concept mentioned in the document, referring to a specific measurement.</data>
