    <node id="Through Hub Threaded Bore">
      <data key="d0">Through Hub Threaded Bore</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Through Hub Threaded Bore is a measurement related to the threaded bore passing through the hub.&lt;SEP&gt;Through hub threaded bore is the bore that runs through the hub of the flange and is threaded.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-de39ca8c7c360d8542b6e7b848f32671&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1359b097a2ba15f87aae6ad689a2a7a9</data>
