    <node id="ASME">
      <data key="d0">ASME</data>
      <data key="d1">organization</data>
      <data key="d2">ASME (American Society of Mechanical Engineers) is a professional organization that develops and publishes standards for pipe flanges and other mechanical components. Specifically, ASME oversees the development and approval of the ASME B16.5 standard, including the ASME B16.5-2013 version. This organization also publishes and maintains the standard documents, such as ASME B16.5-2013, and provides certification for engineers.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-98e40539084cbdf59ac9013514ddab83&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-87960735c6e595f042bd664132512ec0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-94e58312a7e84066f13cc4e7ad9465d9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dacfea17373c5076c30bb104e2de9602&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d633ba5ade581e3474128d750fee5dad&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d9d6f8ad3531ac0840bf5ba01dc89ab8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ab03fc59cd1984b5768de1c8c3e1f065&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-57eadb61afc03dbca89ec4177318d30f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe46a083e9b28534077cc616c7a8fcd2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac011d5da9f248ab56440661b906cb38&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-27138329aa3769f926ca7ebbcd2c8891&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ce8d00c0b7f9fa8976b26a74e2c65e04&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ee003a76b54c8fcc7f20010252b7e38c</data>
      <data key="d4">ASME B16.5-2013.pdf</data>
      <data key="d5">1776329043</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
