      <data key="d0">Dimensions</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Dimensions refer to the physical measurements and specifications of various components, particularly those related to flanges and fittings. These dimensions are discussed extensively throughout the standard, including in both millimeters and inches. Specifically, dimensions cover the measurements and specifications of ring-joint facings, flanges, fittings, and other parts. The ASME B16.5-2013 standard provides detailed measurements for flanges and fittings, including flange edges, raised faces, and center-to-contact surfaces. Dimensions also include diameters, thicknesses, and lengths of various components listed in tables. Both inches and millimeters are used to describe these measurements, ensuring precise specifications for different applications.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-ccbc09bef8fd93e5314dec1dbec481cb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2c1e39e4ae6c4190629baeb4a23e7884&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a6697f0fc19ceac7a699746d339338c6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-efde1d42acf7b7dcd9aa6c8b3872b2cc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f67cfb71cad6bdaadc291b0dfadb7d87&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-47d30b91c8304767d9ee5dee433bb6cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e27122e3377c1128b67882eafcae8b01&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a18d7afa11aad3756a7707e009d78fc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-de39ca8c7c360d8542b6e7b848f32671&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e253e99ebed9a87e642e60132b8f53d9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bca2cf22c89695d4ce65335b23352b32&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9010b0d631cf0ee8f2876c69fd7db43d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e0e55f15f4fdc887c0046610b4244415</data>
      <data key="d4">ASME B16.5-2013.pdf</data>
