    <node id="538°C">
      <data key="d0">538°C</data>
      <data key="d1">temperature</data>
      <data key="d2">538°C is a significant temperature threshold for certain materials, particularly noted in various technical documents and standards. This temperature is specifically mentioned in the ASME B16.5-2013 standard, where it serves as a critical limit for material usage and heat treatment. Additionally, 538°C is referenced in notes and guidelines related to material properties and usage conditions, indicating its importance in ensuring material integrity and performance under specific thermal conditions. Steel carbide, in particular, may undergo a phase change to graphite when exposed to temperatures exceeding this threshold.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-c1c1f70080d9d2a6ea93b5640ca8cea0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0def5c7323fd1839a8729ecb6b306f46&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-82774a230daae46ca5bfd3f0231302b9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ab03fc59cd1984b5768de1c8c3e1f065&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8d3d346cd5a4812cec3f0bbd7f4eec84&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-84c20399bbbf3d7810d504710fe4ed31&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2879e8ce1f305f975a2bf33f2d701842&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe557ad0e335444e461df848f9e28d6b</data>
      <data key="d4">ASME B16.5-2013.pdf</data>
      <data key="d5">1776329045</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Flange Bolt Holes">
      <data key="d0">Flange Bolt Holes</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Flange Bolt Holes are openings in flanges designed for the insertion of bolts. These holes are crucial for securing flanges to pipes or other flanges, ensuring a tight and secure connection. Flange Bolt Holes are specified in various technical contexts, including dimensions and specifications for Class 150 Flanges, and are detailed in the ASME B16.5-2013 standard, specifically in paragraph 6.5 and Table II-17 of Mandatory Appendix II. These holes are essential components in technical specifications, providing precise placement and size guidelines to ensure proper flange assembly and functionality.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-9010b0d631cf0ee8f2876c69fd7db43d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f67cfb71cad6bdaadc291b0dfadb7d87&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4303e33e6d61d4207aeb4ef2e5ef35ea&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-47d30b91c8304767d9ee5dee433bb6cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cbee673be506ab63f82af3e68ebebcd1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a18d7afa11aad3756a7707e009d78fc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-de39ca8c7c360d8542b6e7b848f32671&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-57eadb61afc03dbca89ec4177318d30f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7d620a92f42ccd64b2c87242914a0398&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-97f26dc410df4f859afb6e6e5370b13e</data>
