    <edge source="IHS" target="ASME B16.5-2013">
      <data key="d7">37.0</data>
      <data key="d8">ASME B16.5-2013 is a standard published and licensed by IHS. IHS distributes and licenses the content of ASME B16.5-2013 under a license agreement with ASME International. This standard is provided by IHS under license from ASME International, and IHS distributes the ASME B16.5-2013 document and its copyrighted material under license. Access to ASME B16.5-2013 is provided through IHS under a license from ASME International. IHS also distributes the licensed copy of ASME B16.5-2013 and the licensed content for the standard.</data>
