    <edge source="IHS" target="ASME International">
      <data key="d7">13.0</data>
      <data key="d8">ASME International is responsible for distributing its standards through IHS under license. ASME International holds the copyright for these documents and grants licenses to organizations such as IHS for their distribution. IHS, in turn, provides access to the documents under license from ASME International and ensures their publication under specific conditions. Both ASME International and IHS collaborate to provide material data and standards, with ASME International licensing the data to IHS for publication and distribution. This arrangement allows IHS to distribute ASME standards, including documents like ASME B16.5-2013, under the terms granted by ASME International.</data>
      <data key="d9">content provision,copyright,copyright ownership,distribution,document distribution,license provider,licensing,licensing agreement,organization,publication</data>
      <data key="d10">chunk-e08aa81b5449d47c5a323ae8a58ce735&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e6dd99d0d594bbdd5db11e31461478c9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9010b0d631cf0ee8f2876c69fd7db43d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8e7b456ed825c2e777586a3d95199f23&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8c26f486bf229ab399297201ce84ec2f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-685be4db70f3b18d8a8fac56db2cfaa3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5c8a2582fdf55b244cf7d4892e61cc9f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-82774a230daae46ca5bfd3f0231302b9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e75e86bfb0de38b435f7fe46c6bdc923&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f185747fce944db35b8d0c273257f467&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2879e8ce1f305f975a2bf33f2d701842&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-37d20fead0ece91e4eb35b26f1cd873b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fffc9136a01f33dba4c5242dae862755</data>
